你的 SQL 可以查出 同一個 RefNo 有不同 IsDeleted 的情況，但效能不太好，因為：

1. EXISTS 會自己跟自己比對一次。
2. IN (SELECT...) 巢狀很多層。
3. 你最後其實只想找：
    * 同一個 RefNo
    * 同時存在 IsDeleted=0 和 IsDeleted=1
    * 且這些資料屬於重複 TS_CUST_ID 的客戶

建議改成先把客戶範圍抓出來，再直接用 GROUP BY 找異常。

⸻

Step1. 找出異常 RefNo

;WITH DupCust AS
(
    SELECT DISTINCT SK_CUST_ID
    FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO
    WHERE TS_CUST_ID IN
    (
        SELECT TS_CUST_ID
        FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO
        GROUP BY TS_CUST_ID
        HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
    )
),
TargetCIF AS
(
    SELECT DISTINCT CIF_KEY
    FROM Customer_Migrate_buffer
    WHERE CustomerNo IN
    (
        SELECT SK_CUST_ID
        FROM DupCust
    )
),
BaseData AS
(
    SELECT *
    FROM RP_NP_Migrate_buffer
    WHERE RP = 'BOD'
      AND CIFKEY IN
      (
          SELECT CIF_KEY
          FROM TargetCIF
      )
)
SELECT
    RefNo,
    COUNT(*) AS TotalCnt,
    MIN(IsDeleted) AS MinDeleted,
    MAX(IsDeleted) AS MaxDeleted
FROM BaseData
GROUP BY RefNo
HAVING MIN(IsDeleted) <> MAX(IsDeleted);

這樣可以快速看到：

RefNo	TotalCnt	MinDeleted	MaxDeleted
110101195804164546	2	0	1

代表同一個 RefNo 同時存在有效及刪除資料。

⸻

Step2. 把異常明細撈出來

找到 RefNo 後再看明細：

;WITH DupCust AS
(
    SELECT DISTINCT SK_CUST_ID
    FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO
    WHERE TS_CUST_ID IN
    (
        SELECT TS_CUST_ID
        FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO
        GROUP BY TS_CUST_ID
        HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
    )
),
TargetCIF AS
(
    SELECT DISTINCT CIF_KEY
    FROM Customer_Migrate_buffer
    WHERE CustomerNo IN
    (
        SELECT SK_CUST_ID
        FROM DupCust
    )
),
BaseData AS
(
    SELECT *
    FROM RP_NP_Migrate_buffer
    WHERE RP = 'BOD'
      AND CIFKEY IN
      (
          SELECT CIF_KEY
          FROM TargetCIF
      )
),
BadRefNo AS
(
    SELECT RefNo
    FROM BaseData
    GROUP BY RefNo
    HAVING MIN(IsDeleted) <> MAX(IsDeleted)
)
SELECT *
FROM BaseData
WHERE RefNo IN
(
    SELECT RefNo
    FROM BadRefNo
)
ORDER BY RefNo, IsDeleted;

結果會像：

RefNo              CIFKEY                                  IsDeleted
------------------ -------------------------------------- ----------
110101195804164546 5de499d3-2beb-e511-80c8-0050568c710a   0
110101195804164546 63e499d3-2beb-e511-80c8-0050568c710a   1

⸻

Step3. 找出哪個 TS_CUST_ID 造成的

通常根因分析我會直接這樣查：

SELECT
    A.RefNo,
    A.CIFKEY,
    A.IsDeleted,
    B.CustomerNo,
    C.SK_CUST_ID,
    C.TS_CUST_ID
FROM RP_NP_Migrate_buffer A
INNER JOIN Customer_Migrate_buffer B
    ON A.CIFKEY = B.CIF_KEY
INNER JOIN BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO C
    ON B.CustomerNo = C.SK_CUST_ID
WHERE A.RefNo = '110101195804164546'
ORDER BY C.TS_CUST_ID,A.IsDeleted;

這樣可以直接看到：

RefNo             IsDeleted  SK_CUST_ID   TS_CUST_ID
110101195804164546    0      GOXXE08HK    123456
110101195804164546    1      GOXXE09HK    123456

如果兩筆對應到同一個 TS_CUST_ID，就幾乎可以確定：

* 同一個客戶被拆成兩個 SK_CUST_ID
* 一筆被標記刪除
* 一筆保留
* Migration 時兩筆都被帶進來

⸻

我會怎麼驗證

再做一支統計：

;WITH BaseData AS
(
    SELECT
        RefNo,
        COUNT(DISTINCT IsDeleted) AS DeletedTypeCnt
    FROM RP_NP_Migrate_buffer
    WHERE RP = 'BOD'
    GROUP BY RefNo
)
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM BaseData
WHERE DeletedTypeCnt > 1;

如果結果不是 0，就代表 Migration Source 本身就有矛盾資料。

接著再比對：

SELECT
    RefNo,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CIFKEY) AS CIFCnt,
    COUNT(DISTINCT IsDeleted) AS DeletedCnt
FROM RP_NP_Migrate_buffer
WHERE RP='BOD'
GROUP BY RefNo
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT IsDeleted) > 1;

這支最容易向 SA 或 SK 說明：

同一個 RefNo 被掛在不同 CIF 下，而且 IsDeleted 狀態不一致，因此造成 PB_boardofdirector_fact 出現重複或衝突資料。